key_aboutDescription1: is an advanced, real-time and comprehensive, web and mobile platforms based partograph syatem. It is a comprehensive labor monitoring system build on World Health Organization (WHO) guidelines.
key_aboutDescription2: It enables complete monitoring of women in laor onsite and remotely. With this, you can view charts, get alerts, give directions to staff, stay connected and stay informed about the woman's health and labor conditions.
key_prepartumDescription: Prepartum care helps to decrease risks during delivery and increases the chance of a safe and healthy delivery. This stage observes and monitors mother’s condition prior to labour.
key_latent-description: The first stage of labor monitoring starts with the latent phase. The latent phase is from 0 to 4 cm, and it lasts up to 8 hrs.
key_ActiveStageMonitoringDesc: The active phase is from 4 to 10 cm (full cervical dilatation). It monitors the critical phase of labor.
key_SecondStageMonitoringDesc: The Second-stage of the Partogram monitors the descent and position of the fetal head to predict mode of delivery and obstetric outcome.
key_ThirdStagMonitoringDesc: The third stage of labor begins with the birth of the newborn and ends with the delivery of the placenta and its attached membranes.this stage monitors any complications that may arise.
key_ProductFeatureSubTitle: Easily manage your intrapartum, postpartum parturient until discharged!
key_ProductFeatureSubDesc: arcPartograph application allows recording and storing patient’s data at the point-of-care.
key_recordDetail: Record detailed obstetric issues, past personal and family history, and history of any previous difficult events.
key_measurement: Prepartum, Intrapartum and Postpartum record measurement
key_maintainRecordPost: Maintain past records of discharged patients.
key_RecordarcPartographData: Record arcPartograph data at periodic intervals. Security of retrospective data entry security and share them with peers.
key_internetConnectivity: Capture data even when internet connectivity is not available.
key_plottedAutomatically: The chart is plotted automatically as the data is entered.
key_readingCross: As soon as the readings cross the action and alert lines, alerts are shown onscreen and sent about the labor status.
key_ComprehensivelyMonitorsLabour: Comprehensively monitors labour conditions from Prepartum thru Intrapartum till Postpartum phases when the woman is about to be discharged.
key_laborComplicationsInRealTime: Detecting any labor complications in real-time with alerts to concerned parties.
key_confidantData: Be confidant of data security with no scope of adjusting the chart with retrospective entries.
key_permissionBasedData: Permission based access allows senior doctors to monitor labor jointly and remotely and guide their staff in case of complications.
ket_GetInstantAlerts: Get instant alerts screen, email and text, if labour is not progressing well. Also, on-screen visibility of alerts and of Do’s and Don’ts.
key_applicationIntegration: arcPartography application is open to integration with sensors and other on-site applications.
key_advancedTechnology: arcPartograph, an advanced technology based system, helps reduce labour complications and maternal, fetal and neo-natal morbidities by allowing remote monitoring capabilities.
key_healthcareSystem: It can be used across all levels of the healthcare system for patient information sharing and guidance.
key_Onlinepermission: It provides long-term, on-line, permission based, secure data access for analysis and research.
key_monitoringTool: It is a quality monitoring tool and can be used to measure the excellence of services provided in a labour room.
key_priceOffers: We offer affordable country specific subscription plans to use arcPartograph application.
key_priceSubscript: Please Sign Up to subscribe to plans that meet your needs.
key_FourthStageMonitoringDesc: The fourth stage monitors any post-delivery complications that may occur.
key_PostpartumCareDesc: Postpartum care starts right after the delivery. In arcPartogragh, this stage provides facilities for observations and instructions for mother’s health after labour stages are completed.

partographChart.key_FetalHeartAlertMessageLessThan110: Fetal heart rate has dropped below 110 bpm. Monitor the patient every 5 minutes.
partographChart.key_FetalHeartAlertMessageLessThan100: Fetal heart rate has dropped below 100 bpm. Find out the cause for bradycardia and take appropriate action. Call MO / specialist / Resident / Consultant.
partographChart.key_FetalHeartAlertMessageGreaterThan140: Fetal heart rate has risen above 140 bpm. Monitor the patient every 5 minutes.
partographChart.key_FetalHeartAlertMessageGreaterThan160: Fetal heart rate has risen above 160 bpm. Find out the cause for tachycardia and take appropriate action. Take decision for immediate delivery, instrumental delivery, Emergency LSCS.
